1 RESOLVED BY THE SENATE OF THE STATE OF NEVADA, That for
2 the 36th Special Session of the Nevada Legislature, no allowances
3 will be paid for members of the Senate for periodicals, stamps,
4 stationery or the use of telephones and no allowances will be paid
5 for the President Pro Tempore, Majority Leader, Minority Leader or
6 chair of a committee of the Senate for postage, telephone tolls or
7 other charges for communications; and be it further
8 RESOLVED, That this resolution becomes effective upon
9 adoption.
